ProductTitle: Beats Studio Buds - True Wireless Noise Cancelling - Black
ProductDescription: True wireless noise cancelling Beats Studio Buds are made for music. Designed with a custom acoustic platform,Beats Studio Buds are engineered to deliver powerful,balanced sound in a compact,in-ear form factor. The result: immersive sound that pulls the emotion of music from the studio to your ears to keep you inspired. These earphones feature two listening modes,Active Noise Cancelling (ANC) and Transparency mode,to give you total control of your sound. Each earbud has up to 8 hours of listening time with two additional charges provided by the pocket-sized charging case to give you up to 24 hours of combined playback. Beats Studio Buds also offer simple one-touch pairing for Apple and Android devices.
